    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ is our inner life; He’s in our spirit now;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not far away from us—He’s right inside!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And as we turn to Him and take Him as our all"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He will become in us our inner life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Out from our inner life will come our daily life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And all our living be filled up with Christ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then as we live by Him, He lives His life in us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And He becomes to us our daily life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The real experience of Christ in daily life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will fill the meeting life with Christ Himself."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not empty forms and such, but Christ will be so much;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we will see Him here as the meeting life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Without the inner life there is no daily life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is no meeting life, there is no church!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ as our inner life, Christ in our daily life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will make the meeting life new and glorious!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
